"Someone who knows when you're lost and you're scared. There through the highs and the lows. Someone you count on, someone who cares, besides you wherever you'll go" 
Best friends are rare to find, but I'm so glad that she's mine. This is Marsha, today is her 16th birthday. Why do I call her my best friend? It's not because she's always there whenever I need to poop, it's because she's always there whenever I need her. We've been through a lot together. She never gets bored with my cheesy life stories, when I need to share something, she's all ears. She's a shoulder to cry on, she's also someone I share my laughter with. I'm 110% sure my life would be boring without her presence. I love her so much and I really wish her all the very best in life. Happy birthday to you Swasthi Marsha Hapsari!!!üíñ
